## Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bjornefisk/gitreleasegen.git
cd gitreleasegen
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Lint and format
ruff check .
ruff format .

# Run tests with coverage
pytest --cov=gitreleasegen
```

